-Tomorrow's our
first paying jig.

22:39.793 --> 22:41.728
-That's "gig," you idiot.
-Oh.

22:41.761 --> 22:44.431
-I just had
the strangest dream.
-Will you forget the dream?

22:44.464 --> 22:47.500
We've got to practice
for the Burkowitz bar mitzvah.

22:47.534 --> 22:49.903
-Okay. Let's do it.
-Yeah!

22:49.936 --> 22:54.307
-Here we go! On three.
-Here we go! One, two, three!

